name: Robot Metropolis Carnival Series 5/10
description: The Robot Metropolis Carnival. This is the focused mouse: With all those populating the carnival being dazed, crazed, and innocently kind, one must retain a head that is clear and focused. Created by the fluffy dog in a surprising act of radical intelligence, the mouse pulls the strings necessary to keep the originator, who is the crazed robot, in a neutrally creative track. This ensures less is destroyed and visitors keep coming, and leaving, happy and in one piece.
